Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I keep on trying to find a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:59.23,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok you don't lock the door anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:09.49,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I, you know I never go out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:15.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,And you know that I start to forget things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:22.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok they weren't essential anyway
